Interface PrintChannelService


  • public interface PrintChannelService
    Service for operations related to print channel of Interactive Communication

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      PrintChannel getPrintChannel(String path)
      Get the print channel object given the path.

    • Method Detail

      • getPrintChannel

        PrintChannel getPrintChannel(String path)
                      throws PrintChannelException
        Get the print channel object given the path. Path can point to one of the following
        1. Path of the Interactive Communication like /content/dam/formsanddocuments/ic_name
        2. Path of the actual print channel in Interactive Communication definition like /content/forms/af/ic_name/channels/print
        Parameters:
        path - Path as defined above
        Returns:
        Print channel object if print channel exists
        Throws:
        PrintChannelException - if print channel does not exists at the said path
